It would be better if I can choose the color with keyboard buttons, like with<p><pre><code>    Q W E R T
    A S D F G
</code></pre>
Moving the cursor is really slow and is a disadvantage, especially with a touchpad, however I haven&#x27;t tried on touchscreen.<p>Btw,<p><pre><code>    setInterval(function() {
     var color = document.querySelector(&quot;#kolor-kolor&quot;).style.backgroundColor;
     var links = document.querySelectorAll(&quot;#kolor-options a&quot;);
     for(i in links) {
      if(links[i].style.backgroundColor == color) {
       links[i].click();
       return;
      }
     }
    }, 10);</code></pre>
